  "texts": [
    "However, the virtualization overhead could be further decreased if inter-DPU transfer or direct DRAM-DPU transfer was possible.",
    "In a future version of vPIM, we plan to extend our prototype beyond UPMEM PIM (e.g., adapting our work for [35] and [3]).",
    "NvPIM is the first work that virtualizes a PIM device.",
    "This step is key to bringing PIM to the cloud, the defacto execution infrastructure for companies.",
    "Guest userspaceGuest kernel OverviewAlthough our design is generic, we use Linux KVM [36] (the hypervisor) and Firecracker [12] (the virtual machine monitor) for illustration."
